Prayer is powerful and mighty, the most we can do for him and the others is pray. Pray that if not before, then from now on they trust in Jesus, and if their faith was strong, pray that the Lord gives them the strength and guidance to continue. Evil is in the world, Jesus is the only way to heaven. Our lives are but a vapour and a mist, but eternity is just that. Forever. So I will pray for peace and the love of God to pervade their lives.
